jtorrent.protocols.bittorrent.metainfo

Class Metainfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • jtorrent.protocols.bittorrent.metainfo.Metainfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class Metainfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents a Metainfo file, only containing the required key-value pairs, as specified in the BTP/1.0 standard. For the simplicity of the assignment, Metainfo files will only contain one torrent.
    See Also:
